parameters:
\SE[16]Oh, where am I... I've been transported to another
incomprehensible place again. \SE[15]Maybe it's because I'm
in a dream, but the connections here are all jumbled up...

\SE[4]I can't find anything around here... What should I do?
\SE[3]Should I try going back to a different place?

\SE[68]Huh... Could it be... I'm alone? \SE[45]Did I get
separated from everyone...? \SE[68]I've become a lost
child...?

\SE[16]No, there's no way I would become a lost child.
\SE[64]Everyone here has become a lost child. \SE[16]Well,
there's no helping it... I guess I'll search for them...

\SE[55]Yay... Aisha. \SE[54]We are the Invincible Duo....
\SE[25]Aisha is the best partner.

Vita has learned the secret technique \i[102]Flying Heaven
Dream Bow! \! Furthermore, \i[102]Aisha's bow has evolved
into the Great Bow of Cherry Blossoms!
\SE[4]... How is it? Is this okay?

\SE[7]I'm sorry if that's the limit for now. I'm sure there
were things I wanted to talk about too... \SE[8]But it's all
I can do to materialize...

\SE[16]You don't have to worry about that. You are also a
precious friend made here, after all. \SE[0]If there's
anything I can do, I want to grant any wish you have.

\SE[6]...I pushed myself a little too hard and ended up
exhausted. \!\SE[20]At this rate, I won't be able to help
that child. I need to rest a little more, or I'll just be a
burden.

\SE[3]......\.......\.......\!\SE[62]Could it be... Was this
all part of the plan from the beginning!? To help Vita and
exhaust me in the process...!?

\SE[39]I've been tricked!! What a schemer... such a
terrifying child...!!

\SE[49]... Well, it's fine. \SE[15] I understand how you
feel... and I actually enjoy being manipulated.

\SE[53] (Creating a human body... I tried it for the first
time, but it's so overwhelming. \SE[38] This is no good. I
can never do it again.)

\SE[58] (I haven't really thought about it much, but sexual
reproduction is surprisingly efficient.... \SE[43] The
mysteries of life are truly formidable...)

\SE[4]Ah, I'm tired. I did exercise suddenly, so it's no
wonder. \!\SE[16]...Maybe I should take a little rest.
